    "course_title": "MARKETING ANALYTICS",
    "description": "Impact of analytics on successful marketing decisions. Topics include marketing metrics, digital analytics, marketing response models, segmentation, product design, experimentation and big data. It is designed for students with some background in quantitative methods and an exposure to basic marketing research concepts. A combination of lectures, cases and hands-on model building focused on marketing analytics.",
